dialog.body: Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Walter James. May I have your name, please?
Hello, my name is Donna Miller.
Nice to meet you, Donna. Can you please provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is five six four two eight and my date of birth is zero five dash two zero dash one nine seven eight.
Thank you, Donna. I also need your current address and contact number. Can you please spell out your street address for me?
Of course. My address is S E V E N zero F O U R T Y, Willow Lane.
Thank you for the information, Donna. Is there anything specific you would like assistance with today regarding your policy or coverage?
I'm interested in adding a new vehicle to my policy.
Great! I can assist you with that. Let's discuss the details of the new vehicle so we can update your policy accordingly.
Thank you for your time, Donna. If you need any further assistance, feel free to reach out to us. Have a wonderful day.
